    "This can guide and help to systematize research in the field.Taken together, we think that the insights provided here can both support researchers and practitioners in the field of xAI in the adoption of dialogue-based methods and guide them in the process of choosing architectures and dialogue paradigms, defining objectives and evaluation scenarios, and identifying research questions to study.",
    "Our systematic literature review is unique in addressing dialogue-based xAI approaches, a topic not comprehensively covered in existing literature.",
